title: Night Hospital
description: Click As soon as the lights go out in the hospital, the nurses find themselves caught in a twisted situation. They desperately fight to maintain their sanity, but they become ensnared in an inescapable trap. Slowly succumbing to their lust, they are reduced to meat urinals. "Something strange is entering my body... Ah... No...! I don't want this!"
author: Taegam
